find

public org.ontoware.rdf2go.model.node.URI find(org.ontoware.rdf2go.model.node.URI uri)
Finds an ontology URI for a given URI such a Class, Property or anything related to such an ontology. It uses the Sindice Cache API, loops over the triple-alike results looking for a triple containing which probably is the ontology URI we look for.

Specified by:
find in interface OntologyFinder
Parameters:
uri - the URI we want to find out its ontology
Returns:
the ontology URI
